@startuml
title UML sequence behaviour — Choose language and persist captions default
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #344054
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #344054
  FontColor #101828
}
skinparam package {
  BorderColor #667085
  FontColor #101828
  BackgroundColor #F9FAFB
}
actor "Participant" as person
box "Frontend — Prayer client" #E0F2FE
  participant "CaptionSettings" as settings
  participant "CaptionController" as controller
end box
box "On-device — storage" #FFF4E5
  database "LocalStore" as store
end box

== Choose the caption language ==
person -> settings : Select the caption language from the supported set (L2-047)
settings -> store : Persist the selected language (L2-047)
store --> settings : Saved on the device
settings -> controller : Apply the new language to transcription (L2-047)

== Toggle captions in the room ==
person -> controller : Toggle captions in the room, control per L2-018
controller -> store : Persist the captions default (L2-048)
store --> controller : Saved on the device
note over store : The stored default seeds the green room and the in-room toggle next session (L2-048)
@enduml
